title: C.M. Coffee, Miles City rancher and Stockman Bank exec, dies at 94
text:
Published By: Billings Gazette - Today 
C.M. Coffee, a renowned Eastern Montana rodeo cowboy, businessman and land owner, died Friday of natural causes at age 94, his son confirmed...
